    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.content.DialogInterface.OnCancelListener, android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, GenericDialogInterface

    public class ExpansionPanelGenericPopupDialog
extends GenericPopupDialog
    Performs the expansion panel's ExpansionPanelFactory functionality, which includes Reading and assigning values on load Creation of the sub forms widgets Saving the new selected values to the expansion panel's widget `value` attribute
